race.comment: Small field but terrific contest. BOLD ARTIC (3) may let this all unfold. Wasn't far away fresh over 1000m on the Sunshine Coast and looks suited by the extra ground. Well placed here with the claim and will be winding up strongly. OUR EAGLE ROCK (4) is another in great form. Came home hard to score in the last stride here last time and is drawn for a soft run again. The claiming rider has a great record atop and looks tough to stop again. ATLANTIC RAIN (8) was heavily bet on debut and was far too good, leading throughout and running away with an effortless win. This a big step up but shows good ability and will take catching. SOUTHAVEN (10) resumes and fitter for a trial can feature fresh on best.
